      "blocks": {
        "rich_text_G3qnAM": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Corporate dinners, cocktail parties, anniversaries and birthday parties are always around the corner, invitations are always rolling in. You want to look your absolute best, but last minute styling stress kicks in. If you notice the styles you often admire on others, such as the <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaire-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Solitaire Rings\">solitaire rings</a> adorning manicured hands, it is easy to deduce that it's the jewelry that brings the finishing touch of refinement. Jewelry holds the power to transform outfits from simple to striking, but choosing the right set of jewelry can leave you second guessing. Diamonds are the most versatile choices for party looks! Their brilliance pairs with all types of outfits from a sequined party dress to a colorful evening saree. With a few timeless diamond jewellery styling ideas, you can transform your party look from simple to unforgettable. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mXVxxK": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Match Your Jewellery to the Mood of the Party",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Match Your Jewellery to the Mood of the Party</h2>",
            "custom_id": "mood",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_GiNFiP": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Match_Your_Jewellery_to_the_Mood_of_the_Party.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Every party has its own rhythm. A common mistake while styling outfits is choosing outfits that match the mood of the party, and pairing the usual jewelry that simply goes with the outfit. Your jewelry should match the occasion. Think a timeless <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/solitaires-necklaces\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Solitaire Necklace\">solitaire necklace</a> with a black dress for a corporate gala, trendy jewellery for a friend’s party. You can also order earrings online, like a pair of diamond huggies earrings for a Cocktail Party or a Sangeet night.</p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_9JaN8b": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Brighten Monotone Outfits with Diamonds and Colour",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Brighten Monotone Outfits with Diamonds and Colour</h2>",
            "custom_id": "monotone",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_bpVdgK": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Brighten_Monotone_Outfits_with_Diamonds_and_Colour.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Add sparkle and a pop of color to your monotone outfits with colored online diamond jewellery. Aqua jewellery pendants or toi et moi jewellery rings with pink and blue gemstones bring depth and vibrancy to your look. Create a chic and eye-catching contrast by pairing monotone outfits with colored gemstones. Aqua and blue shades feel regal, pink diamonds are associated with adding a touch of romance, and black diamonds look modern and edgy. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jBjPXC": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Let One Statement Piece Do the Talking",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Let One Statement Piece Do the Talking</h2>",
            "custom_id": "statement",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_PpbCrw": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Let_One_Statement_Piece_Do_the_Talking.jpg",
            "text": "<p>A statement piece is not about excess; it is about focus. It acts as a focal point to the entire look, which is why it is important to keep just one statement piece while the other jewelry should be minimal, creating an ensemble without overwhelming the look. This statement jewelry is the star of your look, a showstopper - a diamond necklace, a <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/tennis-bracelets\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Tennis Bracelet\">tennis bracelet</a> or a unique ring design. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bAL3nR": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>When it comes to party wear jewellery, it is all about the right balance. If you are wearing bold jewellery earrings, skip the heavy necklace; if you are wearing a necklace earring set, keep the diamond rings minimal. This one styling tip can help you create an impeccable party look. </p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_rjpQex": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Match Your Bag and Shoes with Your Jewellery",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Match Your Bag and Shoes with Your Jewellery</h2>",
            "custom_id": "bag",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_Qb8Qem": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Mahila_White.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Styling jewellery for her is all about harmony and details. The way your accessories flow together can make or break a look. The most memorable party looks are the ones that look effortlessly put together. Imagine carrying a sleek white clutch and wearing a white gold diamond necklace set, and pairing these with white strappy pencil heels. This look instantly creates a sense of sync. Men’s jewellery styling follows the same thumb rule of creating cohesion - such as matching the tone of the belt buckle with cuffs and <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/stud-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Stud Earrings\">stud earrings</a>. These small connections elevate your look from ‘dressed’ to ‘styled.’ </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mD3nFF": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Stack Pieces for a Layered Party Look",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Stack Pieces for a Layered Party Look</h2>",
            "custom_id": "stack",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_imH9Qt": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Stacked_Ring.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Layering is a styling secret that can transform casual outfits into party-ready looks! Start with a foundation piece such as a diamond engagement ring and stack slimmer bands around this ring to create depth. Necklaces work beautifully layered, too. A pendant chain layered with a jewellery necklace of a different length frames the neckline elegantly. The layered look feels intentional, detailed and glamorous - perfect for a party look. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": true,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bNLgNB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion </h2><p>Party outfits set the tone according to the theme of the party, but jewellery completes the look. The art of accessorizing is all about balance. Subtle stacks are captivating and even one statement jewelry piece can elevate any look. Creating a cohesive look shows elegance and a keen attention to detail while styling. The key takeaway? It is not just the shine that diamonds bring that makes them perfect for parties, but how each diamond jewellery piece interacts with the outfit and lets you stand out in the crowd. </p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
      },
